  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >a First-person Views Horror Game.</h2></h2>After passing through a Torii gate, you've encountered a small temple which is not been found for several years and there was something sealed inside the temple. You are fallen into a strange place after touching it. There were someones who are not seemed to be a human.<br>There's nothing you have but only an old lantern. From the strange place, you have to escape and return to the real world.<br>The story is motivated by a real urban myth of \"Inunaki tunnel\" and \"A Forgotten Town\"",
